com.soen6441.core.map

Class MapPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soen6441.core.map.MapPoint

  • public class MapPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    The class MapPoint will define a point on the map by its x and y coordinates. It will also provide getter and setter for MapPoint Object. Moreover this class will provide a method "distanceTo" to find the distance from the MapPoint.
    Author:
    Zhe Zhao, Mohammad Ali
